{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"We are drowning in news."},{"time":4000,"text":"Reuters alone puts out"},{"time":6000,"text":"three and a half million news stories a year."},{"time":8000,"text":"That's just one source."}]},{"cues":[{"time":11000,"text":"My question is: How many of those stories"},{"time":13000,"text":"are actually going to matter in the long run?"},{"time":16000,"text":"That's the idea behind The Long News."},{"time":19000,"text":"It's a project by The Long Now Foundation,"},{"time":21000,"text":"which was founded by TEDsters including"},{"time":23000,"text":"Kevin Kelly and Stewart Brand."},{"time":25000,"text":"And what we're looking for is news stories that might still matter"},{"time":27000,"text":"50 or 100 or 10,000 years from now."},{"time":31000,"text":"And when you look at the news through that filter,"},{"time":34000,"text":"a lot falls by the wayside."}]},{"cues":[{"time":37000,"text":"To take the top stories from the A.P. this last year,"},{"time":40000,"text":"is this going to matter in a decade?"},{"time":43000,"text":"Or this?"},{"time":45000,"text":"Or this?"},{"time":48000,"text":"Really?"},{"time":50000,"text":"Is this going to matter in 50 or 100 years?"},{"time":54000,"text":"Okay, that was kind of cool."},{"time":56000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":58000,"text":"But the top story of this past year was the economy,"},{"time":60000,"text":"and I'm just betting that, sooner or later,"},{"time":63000,"text":"this particular recession is going to be old news."}]},{"cues":[{"time":66000,"text":"So, what kind of stories might"},{"time":68000,"text":"make a difference for the future?"},{"time":71000,"text":"Well, let's take science."},{"time":74000,"text":"Someday, little robots will go"},{"time":76000,"text":"through our bloodstreams fixing things."},{"time":78000,"text":"That someday is already here if you're a mouse."},{"time":80000,"text":"Some recent stories:"},{"time":82000,"text":"nanobees zap tumors with real bee venom;"},{"time":85000,"text":"they're sending genes into the brain;"},{"time":88000,"text":"a robot they built that can crawl through the human body."}]},{"cues":[{"time":92000,"text":"What about resources? How are we going to feed nine billion people?"},{"time":95000,"text":"We're having trouble feeding six billion today."},{"time":98000,"text":"As we heard yesterday, there's over a billion people hungry."},{"time":101000,"text":"Britain will starve without genetically modified crops."},{"time":105000,"text":"Bill Gates, fortunately, has bet a billion on [agricultural] research."}]},{"cues":[{"time":110000,"text":"What about global politics?"},{"time":112000,"text":"The world's going to be very different when and if China sets the agenda,"},{"time":115000,"text":"and they may."},{"time":117000,"text":"They've overtaken the U.S. as the world's biggest car market,"},{"time":120000,"text":"they've overtaken Germany as the largest exporter,"},{"time":124000,"text":"and they've started doing DNA tests on kids"},{"time":126000,"text":"to choose their careers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":129000,"text":"We're finding all kinds of ways to push back the limits of what we know."},{"time":132000,"text":"Some recent discoveries:"},{"time":134000,"text":"There's an ant colony from Argentina that has now"},{"time":136000,"text":"spread to every continent but Antarctica;"},{"time":140000,"text":"there's a self-directed robot scientist that's made a discovery --"},{"time":143000,"text":"soon, science may no longer need us,"},{"time":146000,"text":"and life may no longer need us either;"},{"time":148000,"text":"a microbe wakes up after 120,000 years."},{"time":151000,"text":"It seems that with or without us,"},{"time":153000,"text":"life will go on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":155000,"text":"But my pick for the top Long News story of this past year"},{"time":157000,"text":"was this one: water found on the moon."},{"time":160000,"text":"Makes it a lot easier to put a colony up there."},{"time":163000,"text":"And if NASA doesn't do it, China might,"},{"time":165000,"text":"or somebody in this room might write a big check."}]},{"cues":[{"time":168000,"text":"My point is this:"},{"time":170000,"text":"In the long run, some news stories"},{"time":172000,"text":"are more important than others."},{"time":174000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}